2
00:00:01,940 --> 00:00:03,800
When a giant Chinese corporation

3
00:00:03,800 --> 00:00:04,980
goes bankrupt,

4
00:00:04,980 --> 00:00:07,240
should the Chinese government bail it out,

5
00:00:07,240 --> 00:00:08,660
or let it fail?

6
00:00:08,660 --> 00:00:10,930
In the case of Anbang Insurance Group,

7
00:00:10,930 --> 00:00:13,080
